"""test_orderOfMagnitude doc..."""
testOrder = -9
while testOrder < 10:
    for i in range(25):
        v = random.uniform(1.0, 9.9) * math.pow(10.0, testOrder)
        result = value.order_of_magnitude(v)
        msg = 'Invalid Order %s != %s (%s)' % (result, testOrder, v)
        self.assertEqual(testOrder, result, msg)
    testOrder += 1
